description:
The first Oracle APEX meetup will go over the concept of the meetups and as first topic APEX 5.0 will be covered.

We'll have an "Open Mic" too, so anybody can get on stage for 5 minutes and show what they did or share their ideas.

Come to the meetup - it's a great place to network and enjoy pizza :)

The meetup is completely free.

Agenda

16.00  Registration

16.30  Outline concept APEX Meet-up

16.45  Presentation APEX 5.0

18.00  Pizza break, Networking and "Open Mic"

21.00  End
name: First Belgium APEX Meetup

description:
New topics to be decided.

If you have an interesting topic you want to discuss, don't hesitate to bring it forward.

Come back later for more details, but already block the date in your agenda!
name: ORCLAPEX-BE meetup 19-11-2014
